## Useful Skills (curated)

Your curated list of skills. Skills cascade automatically from the plugins you have installed — this section is just "these are the ones I reach for often, in roughly these situations."

Organize by workflow stage:

### Planning & thinking
- `superpowers:brainstorming` — explore requirements before implementation
- `compound-engineering:ce-plan` — multi-step plans

### Research
- `compound-engineering:research:framework-docs-researcher` — official docs for frameworks

### Dev workflow
- `{{YOUR_TEAM_PLUGIN}}:issue-to-draft-pr` — ticket → plan → implement → PR

### PR/commit management
- `pr-status` — check PR status and CI

### Communication
- `slack:standup` — generate standup from recent Slack activity

### Debugging & verification
- `superpowers:systematic-debugging` — before proposing fixes

### Where new skills live

Document the hierarchy of skill locations you use:

| Location | Scope |
|---|---|
| `~/repos/{{TEAM_PLUGIN}}/` | Team, everywhere |
| `~/.claude/skills/` | Personal, everywhere |
| `~/repos/harambe/.claude/skills/` | Harambe only |
| `<repo>/.claude/skills/` | That repo only |

